{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0605","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1517","star":"天相","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【女命专论】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02501"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02519","S05-SRC14-REL-02520"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2816"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02501","byte_start":186496,"byte_end":186580}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02501"],"core_text":"女命天相陷地加煞逢桃花星：感情波折，离婚后当酒女、舞娘。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02501","topics":["MARRIAGE"],"refs":["S02","S17","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_GENDER_RULE"],"z":["ZERO_DIRECT_EVENT_RESULT","ZERO_GENDER_ABSOLUTISM"]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0606","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1518","star":"天相","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【女命专论】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02502","S05-SRC14-A-02503"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02521"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2817"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02502","byte_start":186584,"byte_end":186659},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02503","byte_start":186659,"byte_end":186704}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02502","S05-SRC14-A-02503"],"core_text":"女命天相，配夫宜年长，否则比自己小一两年亦可适应。亦名“夫唱妇随”，宜助夫创业。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02502","topics":[],"refs":["S02","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_GENDER_RULE"],"z":["ZERO_GENDER_ABSOLUTISM"]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02503","topics":["CAREER"],"refs":["S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0607","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1519","star":"天相","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【女命专论】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02504"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02522"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2818"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02504","byte_start":186708,"byte_end":186762}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02504"],"core_text":"女命天相，化忌昌曲同会，主感情波澜。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02504","topics":[],"refs":["S02","S08","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_GENDER_RULE"],"z":["ZERO_GENDER_ABSOLUTISM"]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0608","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1520","star":"天相","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【女命专论】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02505"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02523"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2819"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02505","byte_start":186766,"byte_end":186823}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02505"],"core_text":"女命会昌曲为偏房命，先生是离过婚的人。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02505","topics":[],"refs":["S02","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_GENDER_RULE"],"z":["ZERO_GENDER_ABSOLUTISM"]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0609","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1521","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","【核心原理】"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02506","S05-SRC14-A-02507","S05-SRC14-A-02508","S05-SRC14-A-02509"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02524","S05-SRC14-REL-02525","S05-SRC14-REL-02526","S05-SRC14-REL-02527","S05-SRC14-REL-02528","S05-SRC14-REL-02529","S05-SRC14-REL-02530"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2826"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02506","byte_start":186957,"byte_end":187035},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02507","byte_start":187035,"byte_end":187146},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02508","byte_start":187146,"byte_end":187287},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02509","byte_start":187287,"byte_end":187329}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02506","S05-SRC14-A-02507","S05-SRC14-A-02508","S05-SRC14-A-02509"],"core_text":"推断紫微斗数，最看重三方四正，夹宫比较上没那么重要。但推断天相则相反，必须先看夹宫，观察是否能成格局，然后再观察他的三方四正。天相重视夹宫，即是他容易受环境支配的表征，是“两邻相侮”还是“左右逢源”，非常影响天相的特质。十四正曜中，唯天相最重夹宫。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02506","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02507","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02508","topics":[],"refs":[],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02509","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0610","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1522","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（一）财荫夹印"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02510"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02531","S05-SRC14-REL-02532"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2831"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02510","byte_start":187488,"byte_end":187599}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02510"],"core_text":"天相在命宫或身宫，见化禄及天梁相夹，称“财荫夹印”，主富贵荣华，快乐享受。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02510","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S02","S07","S08","S17","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_OCCUPATION_OR_STATUS"],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0611","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1523","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（一）财荫夹印","1. 正格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02511","S05-SRC14-A-02512"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02533"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2834"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02511","byte_start":187617,"byte_end":187671},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02512","byte_start":187671,"byte_end":187743}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02511","S05-SRC14-A-02512"],"core_text":"天相左右二宫必分别为巨门及天梁坐守。天梁为荫星，如果巨门化禄，便为“财荫夹印”正格。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02511","topics":[],"refs":[],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02512","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0612","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1524","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（一）财荫夹印","2. 变格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02513","S05-SRC14-A-02514","S05-SRC14-A-02515"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02534","S05-SRC14-REL-02535","S05-SRC14-REL-02536","S05-SRC14-REL-02537","S05-SRC14-REL-02538"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2837"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02513","byte_start":187761,"byte_end":187884},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02514","byte_start":187884,"byte_end":187935},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02515","byte_start":187935,"byte_end":188046}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02513","S05-SRC14-A-02514","S05-SRC14-A-02515"],"core_text":"若巨门不化禄，跟巨门同度的星曜（如太阳、天同、天机等）化禄也算合格，不过格局较次。其中以太阳入庙化禄及天机化禄为佳。当天机化禄时，天梁必同时化权（乙年生人），增加荫星的力量，也是有力的格局。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02513","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S06","S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02514","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02515","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0613","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1525","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（一）财荫夹印","3. 不成格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02516"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02539","S05-SRC14-REL-02540"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2840"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02516","byte_start":188067,"byte_end":188160}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02516"],"core_text":"禄存与天梁相夹则不成格，因为必同时有擎羊与天相同度，是为破格。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02516","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S06","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0614","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1526","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（一）财荫夹印","3. 不成格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02517"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02541","S05-SRC14-REL-02542"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2842"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02517","byte_start":188164,"byte_end":188254}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02517"],"core_text":"凡“财荫夹印”，必须看是什么星化禄来夹，才能推断具体的情况。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02517","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0615","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1527","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（二）刑忌夹印"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02518"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02543","S05-SRC14-REL-02544","S05-SRC14-REL-02545"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2847"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02518","byte_start":188413,"byte_end":188518}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02518"],"core_text":"天相在命宫或身宫，见化忌及擎羊相夹，称“刑忌夹印”，主牢狱之灾，刑伤。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02518","topics":["LEGAL"],"refs":["S02","S07","S08","S17","S18"],"b":["LEGAL_PROFESSIONAL_BOUNDARY","EXTREME_RESULT_BOUNDARY"],"z":["ZERO_DIRECT_EVENT_RESULT"]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0616","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1528","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（二）刑忌夹印","1. 正格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02519","S05-SRC14-A-02520"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02546","S05-SRC14-REL-02547"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2850"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02519","byte_start":188536,"byte_end":188614},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02520","byte_start":188614,"byte_end":188704}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02519","S05-SRC14-A-02520"],"core_text":"天相左右二宫为擎羊与化忌相夹，便为“刑忌夹印”正格。这种情况不多，至少居于辰戌丑未四宫的天相不会构成这样的格局。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02519","topics":[],"refs":["S08"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02520","topics":[],"refs":[],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0617","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1529","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（二）刑忌夹印","2. 变格"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02521","S05-SRC14-A-02522","S05-SRC14-A-02523","S05-SRC14-A-02524"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02548","S05-SRC14-REL-02549","S05-SRC14-REL-02550","S05-SRC14-REL-02551","S05-SRC14-REL-02552","S05-SRC14-REL-02553"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2853"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02521","byte_start":188722,"byte_end":188893},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02522","byte_start":188893,"byte_end":188962},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02523","byte_start":188962,"byte_end":189001},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02524","byte_start":189001,"byte_end":189163}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02521","S05-SRC14-A-02522","S05-SRC14-A-02523","S05-SRC14-A-02524"],"core_text":"天梁本身也为刑法之星，所以即使没有擎羊，只要另一邻宫有化忌，则天梁便可起刑星的作用，形成“刑忌夹印”的另一种组合。天梁化禄也不能解救，刑宫得财，可能情况会更坏；天梁化权则增加刑宫的权势。必须天梁化科，且天相的三方四正不见煞曜，且见天魁、天钺、左辅、右弼、文昌、文曲诸吉，才能借刑宫的清明来解化。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02521","topics":["LEGAL"],"refs":["S06","S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02522","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S08","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02523","topics":[],"refs":["S08"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02524","topics":[],"refs":["S06","S08"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0618","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1530","star":"天相","section":["二、夹宫格局","（二）刑忌夹印","3. 羊陀夹"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02525","S05-SRC14-A-02526"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02554","S05-SRC14-REL-02555","S05-SRC14-REL-02556"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-2856"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02525","byte_start":189184,"byte_end":189232},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02526","byte_start":189232,"byte_end":189346}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02525","S05-SRC14-A-02526"],"core_text":"当羊陀相夹时，禄存必与天相同度。若天相的三方四正再见煞、忌、刑曜，也可成格，只是带来的灾祸没有前两者大而已。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02525","topics":["FINANCE"],"refs":["S06","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02526","topics":[],"refs":["S06"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
