{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0665","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1653","star":"天梁","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【基本特质】","3. 荫庇的意义"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02728","S05-SRC14-A-02729"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02812","S05-SRC14-REL-02813","S05-SRC14-REL-02814","S05-SRC14-REL-02815","S05-SRC14-REL-02816"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-3110"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02728","byte_start":206719,"byte_end":206788},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02729","byte_start":206788,"byte_end":206929}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02728","S05-SRC14-A-02729"],"core_text":"天梁的消灾解厄，含有灾难先来然后得化解的意味。所以必先经危难然后平安，先有病患然后痊愈，先无凭借然后得人扶助，先觉精神空虚，然后寄托于宗教。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02728","topics":[],"refs":[],"b":[],"z":[]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02729","topics":["HEALTH"],"refs":["S02","S17","S18"],"b":["MEDICAL_PROFESSIONAL_BOUNDARY"],"z":["ZERO_MEDICAL_DIAGNOSIS"]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
{"id":"S05-SRC14-PROJ-S05-0666","cg":"S05-SRC14-CG-1654","star":"天梁","section":["一、核心属性与基本特质","【基本特质】","3. 荫庇的意义"],"core":["S05-SRC14-A-02730","S05-SRC14-A-02731"],"context":[],"format":[],"relations":["S05-SRC14-REL-02817","S05-SRC14-REL-02818","S05-SRC14-REL-02819","S05-SRC14-REL-02820","S05-SRC14-REL-02821","S05-SRC14-REL-02822","S05-SRC14-REL-02823"],"lines":["S05-SRC14-LINE-3111"],"spans":[{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02730","byte_start":206936,"byte_end":207095},{"source_atom_id":"S05-SRC14-A-02731","byte_start":207095,"byte_end":207287}],"roots":["S05-SRC14-A-02730","S05-SRC14-A-02731"],"core_text":"由荫庇这层意义，可以引伸为刑法纪律（刑法保障善良百姓），因此天梁可表征为民伸冤除害的清官，犹如包拯、海瑞。由此引伸为监察之职，许多核数师、监事理事，或商务上的市场计划、财务计划人才，命宫或事业宫皆见天梁，盖天梁的监察有退居幕后的意味。","context_text":"","routes":[{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02730","topics":["LEGAL"],"refs":["S02","S17","S18"],"b":["HISTORICAL_OCCUPATION_OR_STATUS"],"z":["ZERO_HISTORICAL_OCCUPATION_DIRECT_MAPPING"]},{"a":"S05-SRC14-A-02731","topics":["CAREER"],"refs":["S07","S17","S18"],"b":[],"z":[]}],"context_contribution":"NO","direct_event":"NO","direct_endpoint":"NO","direct_score":"NO","relation_target_bundle_status":"PASS","relation_target_added_ids":[],"external_raw_dependency":"NO","embedded_raw_runtime_dependency":"NO","base_contribution_owner_count":1}
